Package giovynet.devices Description

Provides classes for manipulating Giovynet.com devices.

  • Refer to Giovynet Java Electronic Solution Here.

Package Specification

This package is designed to work with J2SE or higher, this package is used for to communicate, to send and receive data and instructions from Giovyenet.com devices, works on operating systems Windows (tested in: XP, Vista and 7) and Linux (tested in: Ubuntu 8.04 or higher).
  • Refer to any framemaker specification here.

Related Documentation

For overviews, tutorials, examples, guides, and tool documentation, please see:
  • www.giovynet.com
